OL,4,CArgos sorry for '3 for 2' toy confusion
OL,5, Argos has apologised for confusion over
OL,6, prices on toys included in a "3 for 2"
OL,7, offer.
OL,9,FCustomers accused the company of
OL,10,Fpushing prices up as soon as the offer
OL,11,Fwas made available.
OL,13,FBut Argos said the toys in question had
OL,14,Fpreviously been sold for promotional
OL,15,Fprices and had now returned to their
OL,16,Fnormal price.
OL,18,FIt said it had not clearly marked that
OL,19,Fsome of its toys were on promotion "due
OL,20,Fto a technical issue".
